text: Kudashevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Imangulovsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 377 as of 2010. There are 10 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Uchaly, 12 km from Imangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Kudashevo, Uchalinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
